# Styling

This project uses Tailwind CSS for styling.

- Tailwind CSS is configured via the `@tailwindcss/vite` plugin in [coderx/vite.config.ts](mdc:coderx/vite.config.ts).
- The Tailwind configuration file is likely [tailwind.config.js](mdc:tailwind.config.js).
- Global styles and Tailwind directives are likely defined in [coderx/src/index.css](mdc:coderx/src/index.css).
